{
  "stem": "945.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My younger brother and I, [SOBBING], we said, no, we are not going to be beggars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we started venturing out into the country again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And little by little we were strong enough to start doing some work, and we were given some food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the same countryside and to some of the same people, and they were kind to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, of course, we weren't scared to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were good workers, and they knew us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, like I said before, I have to say that a lot of the Ukrainian local people were feeling sorry for us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just as there were many that were out and out killers, there were some that were honest and good human beings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, they, too, started to feel the effects of the Romanian and the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, we started to struggle, and we didn't want to give up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then my dad got a little stronger, and he, too, started going out again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we started hearing of a reversal of maybe the war starting to change in favor of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard that because the Romanians had newspapers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they allowed, once in a while, newspapers to come into to Shargorod and to the other areas and word spread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's amazing how sometimes these things spread without anybody knowing how they spread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's like a wind that brings news, brings music from a distance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we heard that the Russians were getting close to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were getting close to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Germans were facing defeats in, in many areas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were starting to hope that maybe someday we might be a liberated again, and we might survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly Romanian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
